/*
// Definition for a Node.
class Node {
    public int val;
    public Node left;
    public Node right;

    public Node() {}

    public Node(int _val) {
        val = _val;
    }

    public Node(int _val,Node _left,Node _right) {
        val = _val;
        left = _left;
        right = _right;
    }
};
*/
class Solution {
    public Node treeToDoublyList(Node root) {
        if (root == null) {
            return null;
        }
        Node head = new Node();
        Node index = head;
        // 中序遍历中完成指针的绑定
        Stack<Node> stack = new Stack<>();
        while(root != null || !stack.isEmpty()) {
            if (root != null) {
                stack.push(root);
                root = root.left;
            } else if (!stack.isEmpty()) {
                root = stack.pop();
                index.right = root;
                root.left = index;

                index = root;
                root = root.right;
            }
        }

        index.right = head.right;
        head.right.left = index;
    
        return head.right;
    }
}
